Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.93,Default,A,0,0,0,,明明寫著車站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.93,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(716,654)}Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:50.33,Default,A,0,0,0,,再說了 這地圖也太簡陋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.33,Default,A,0,0,0,,這樣根本看不明白呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.93,Default,A,0,0,0,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:13.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.82,Default,A,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:26.55,Default,A,0,0,0,,這是妳的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:28.55,Default,A,0,0,0,,妳也是新月學園的新生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:30.55,Default,A,0,0,0,,現在要去辦開學典禮的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.71,Default,A,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:36.13,Default,A,0,0,0,,要獨自一人去魔女的學校 還是有點怕怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.26,Default,A,0,0,0,,我是亞可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:40.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,從我六歲時看了閃耀夏莉奧的魔法秀以來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,我一直夢想成為一位魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.26,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(676,654)}Akko
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:45.06,Default,A,0,0,0,,不如說 這是超越夢想的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:47.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,妳當然認識吧 閃耀夏莉奧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,瞧 夏莉奧的稀有卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.48,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(736,654)}Rare Card
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,我的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,在魔法界裡 夏莉奧也非常有影響力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:58.97,Default,A,0,0,0,,在我的周圍 完全沒人喜歡夏莉奧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.82,Default,A,0,0,0,,他們總是吐槽我「妳在說哪個年代事情」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.71,Default,A,0,0,0,,那麼厲害的事 夏莉奧以外沒人能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:07.84,Default,A,0,0,0,,畢竟她連月…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:19.04,Default,A,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.73,Default,A,0,0,0,,傀儡魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.73,Default,A,0,0,0,,頭一次親眼見到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:27.64,Default,A,0,0,0,,乖 乖 到這邊來 不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.62,Default,A,0,0,0,,眼睛 我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.04,Default,A,0,0,0,,等等 這太過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.73,Default,A,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:43.37,Default,A,0,0,0,,妳叫什麼名字？ 剛才是怎麼做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:48.17,Default,A,0,0,0,,我也郵購了魔法教材 但是完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.48,Default,A,0,0,0,,都不知道有沒有打好基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.46,Default,A,0,0,0,,不過到了學校裡學習之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:55.64,Default,A,0,0,0,,也不知能不能用出夏莉奧那樣的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.15,Default,A,0,0,0,,請…請問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.37,Default,A,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:07.86,Default,A,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,討厭 討厭 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:29.88,Default,A,0,0,0,,真是的 那傢伙是怎麼回事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:37.26,Default,A,0,0,0,,新月學園的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,春假過得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,無論去哪裡都全是遊客 擠死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來在今天開學典禮入學的新生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有一人不是來自魔女家族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 最近一般人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,最近因為學校的經營困難的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,說是不得不讓非魔女家族入學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,新月學園的品格都被拉低了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,連掃帚都騎不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,騎不了掃帚的魔女 在新月學園的歷史裡是從未有過的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.95,Default,A,0,0,0,,卡嘉莉 敦子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.95,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(599,650)}篝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.08,Default,A,0,0,0,,是新生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 就是妳呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.06,Default,A,0,0,0,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.97,Default,A,0,0,0,,能快點來就好了 巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,巴士？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.60,Default,A,0,0,0,,欸 這裡不是巴士站嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,妳覺得這裡會有巴士來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Tia Fraere
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是掃帚的車站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,靈脈節點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:40.77,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,654)}Leyline Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,從這裡由靈脈連接著新月學園
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,靈脈從太古時起就運輸著魔法的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,乘著這股能量就可以飛到新月學園去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是魔法的高速路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.46,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\pos(750,654)}Highway
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這是魔女的基礎知識喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要是在開學典禮時遲到的話 會被魔法界永久驅逐的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.53,Default,A,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:42.84,Default,l,0,0,0,,哇 已經要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.08,Default,L,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:51.08,Default,L,0,0,0,,媽媽和老姐讓我帶的行李真是太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:51.08,TopLeft,L,0,0,0,,註：「老姐」這裡是個人名，不確定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:55.75,Default,L,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.93,Default,L,0,0,0,,Tia F…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:07.82,Default,L,0,0,0,,妳…妳不去嗎？ 開學典禮就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.06,Default,L,0,0,0,,沒見過的新面孔呀 妳是新生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.48,Default,L,0,0,0,,新月學園的校規十分嚴厲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:18.82,Default,L,0,0,0,,要是遲到了的話就進不去囉 直接退學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.82,Default,A,0,0,0,,我沒有掃帚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:23.44,Default,A,0,0,0,,而且就算有也騎不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.28,Default,L,0,0,0,,抱歉 我要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:32.55,Default,L,0,0,0,,要坐上來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:37.36,Default,L,0,0,0,,我沒試過載人 但是試試看說不定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:39.50,Default,A,0,0,0,,真的嗎 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.58,Default,A,0,0,0,,這世上也是有友善的魔女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.58,Default,A,0,0,0,,我叫卡嘉莉敦子 叫我亞可就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.58,Comment,A,0,0,0,,{\pos(774,654)} Akko
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:46.09,Default,L,0,0,0,,我…我叫洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:46.09,Comment,L,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,654)}Lotte
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.88,Default,L,0,0,0,,趕快 我們沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:48.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:51.74,Default,L,0,0,0,,那我們就出發囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:52.41,Default,A,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.84,Default,L,0,0,0,,飛吧 我的掃帚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.20,Default,L,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Tia Fraere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.26,Default,A,0,0,0,,騙人 騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.14,Default,A,0,0,0,,飛了 飛了 飛了 飛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.52,Default,L,0,0,0,,看起來行李有點太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:13.78,Default,L,0,0,0,,打開吧 前往新月學園的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:18.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,這是什麼 這是什麼 這是什麼 這是什麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.05,Default,A,0,0,0,,果然還是不行 不行 放我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.70,Default,L,0,0,0,,稍微老實一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:33.42,Default,A,0,0,0,,行李…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:40.81,Default,S,0,0,0,,說到傳說之森阿爾克圖拉斯 尋常的魔女是無法進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:40.81,Comment,S,0,0,0,,{\pos(533,654)}Arcturus
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:40.81,TopLeft,,0,0,0,,Arcturus 即大角星 牧夫座的α星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.82,Default,L,0,0,0,,從來沒有這樣過 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:54.36,Default,L,0,0,0,,難道說妳帶著鹽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:55.44,Default,A,0,0,0,,鹽？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.61,Default,L,0,0,0,,靈脈討厭鹽分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:02.86,Default,A,0,0,0,,是這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:04.26,Default,L,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:05.54,Default,A,0,0,0,,梅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:06.57,Default,L,0,0,0,,快扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:09.53,Default,A,0,0,0,,我沒有梅乾就活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.86,Default,L,0,0,0,,求妳了 快扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.86,Default,A,0,0,0,,我 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.52,Default,A,0,0,0,,我的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.60,Default,L,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:25.85,Default,A,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.28,Default,U,0,0,0,,怎麼了 阿爾克爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.28,Comment,U,0,0,0,,{\pos(701.714,654)}Alcor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.28,TopLeft,U,0,0,0,,Alcor 北斗六的伴星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.62,Default,U,0,0,0,,難道說去了阿爾克圖拉斯之森？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.93,Default,A,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.73,Default,A,0,0,0,,我的寶貝兒沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.12,Default,A,0,0,0,,死…死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.90,Default,S,0,0,0,,煩人透頂說的就是妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.46,Default,A,0,0,0,,還…還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.46,Default,S,0,0,0,,魔女不會這麼簡單的死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.13,Default,L,0,0,0,,洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:45.22,Default,A,0,0,0,,沒事吧 沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.66,Default,L,0,0,0,,我沒事 但是掃帚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.24,Default,S,0,0,0,,看樣子我們已經到了目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.96,Default,A,0,0,0,,目的地？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.46,Default,A,0,0,0,,那…這裡就是新月學園？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.34,Default,A,0,0,0,,開學典禮呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.77,Default,L,0,0,0,,不是 這裡只是陌生的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.81,Default,S,0,0,0,,阿爾克圖拉斯之森
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.65,Default,L,0,0,0,,阿爾克圖拉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.10,Default,K,0,0,0,,不是吧 禁忌的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.28,Default,A,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:18.72,Default,L,0,0,0,,是在古老傳說中的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.61,Default,L,0,0,0,,是被魔法樹保護的神聖之地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:25.36,Default,L,0,0,0,,傳說一旦被迷惑了 就算是魔女也很難逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:29.22,Default,A,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣 開學典禮要趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:32.29,Default,S,0,0,0,,不說這個 妳說不定一生都會被困在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:35.05,Default,A,0,0,0,,我說 妳別嚇唬我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:39.74,Default,A,0,0,0,,找到我丟的行李了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.53,Default,L,0,0,0,,亞可 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.73,Default,L,0,0,0,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.69,Default,A,0,0,0,,那是什麼鬼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.44,Default,S,0,0,0,,是曼達拉草 食人植物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.44,Comment,S,0,0,0,,{\pos(580.571,654)}Mandrake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.64,Default,S,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:20.50,Default,S,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.13,Default,A,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:23.97,Default,S,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.55,Default,S,0,0,0,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.12,Default,A,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.51,Default,S,0,0,0,,在這站好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.53,Default,S,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Juras Haras Haras
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.83,Default,A,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.40,Default,S,0,0,0,,念咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:42.71,Default,A,0,0,0,,咒語？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.36,Default,L,0,0,0,,念的話就能找到回去的路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.65,Default,S,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kutchur Katela Flala
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.86,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kutchur Kat… F Fla fla?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.24,Default,S,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kutchur Katela Flala
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.08,Default,S,0,0,0,,腹腔用力 大聲念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.44,Default,A,0,0,0,,Kutchur Katela Flala
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.76,Default,A,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.59,Default,A,0,0,0,,妳好~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:26.82,Default,A,0,0,0,,這是什麼 剛才的咒語是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:30.49,Default,S,0,0,0,,意思是 「笨蛋 不服的話來吃掉我吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.28,Default,A,0,0,0,,蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:35.22,Default,S,0,0,0,,這是仅棲息在阿爾克圖拉斯之森的傳說中的雞蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:35.22,Comment,S,0,0,0,,{\pos(994.286,654)}Cockatrice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.25,Default,S,0,0,0,,據說羽毛上有著劇毒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:41.26,Default,S,0,0,0,,對於一個劇毒收藏家來說是超稀有的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.96,Default,S,0,0,0,,妳們去吸引它的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.25,Default,S,0,0,0,,我會趁機去取得它的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:47.84,Default,A,0,0,0,,蛤？ 也就是把我們當誘餌嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.63,Default,S,0,0,0,,不對 是祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.88,Default,S,0,0,0,,再念一遍剛才的「咒語」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.47,Default,A,0,0,0,,怎麼可能念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.06,Default,S,0,0,0,,就是這樣 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:03.02,Default,S,0,0,0,,如果中了那傢伙的吐息的話 會變成石頭的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.27,Default,A,0,0,0,,石頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.11,Default,A,0,0,0,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.74,Default,S,0,0,0,,到手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.42,Default,A,0,0,0,,停…停不下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.02,Default,A,0,0,0,,妳還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:42.89,Default,L,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:45.10,Default,A,0,0,0,,我們得快點走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:48.95,Default,A,0,0,0,,再磨蹭的話 開學典禮要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:49.65,Default,L,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.28,Default,L,0,0,0,,我的腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.38,Default,L,0,0,0,,不行了 我們趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:56.74,Default,A,0,0,0,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.33,Default,A,0,0,0,,我絕不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.70,Default,A,0,0,0,,不能再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.21,Default,A,0,0,0,,我要成為魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.05,Default,A,0,0,0,,如果向前伸手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.92,Default,A,0,0,0,,就會一觸即發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.01,Default,A,0,0,0,,令人緊張的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.47,Default,A,0,0,0,,令人興奮的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.37,Default,A,0,0,0,,只屬於我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:34.31,Default,A,0,0,0,,這是… 夏莉奧的魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.59,Default,A,0,0,0,,洛蒂 躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.54,Default,L,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.09,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kutchur Katela Flala!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:59.14,Default,A,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:03.13,Default,A,0,0,0,,小鬼啊 看過來 向著拍手的聲音來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:03.13,TopLeft,A,0,0,0,,日本兒童遊戲中用來嘲諷的台詞\N鬼さんこちら 手の鳴る方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.00,Default,A,0,0,0,,上鈎了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.09,Default,S,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:41.05,Default,S,0,0,0,,坐上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:49.21,Default,A,0,0,0,,謝謝 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:52.77,Default,S,0,0,0,,我叫蘇西 蘇西 曼芭芭拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:52.77,Comment,S,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,654)}Sucy      Manbavaran
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:55.08,Default,A,0,0,0,,謝謝 蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.80,Default,A,0,0,0,,真是難纏的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.16,Default,L,0,0,0,,載著三個人的話跑不掉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:11.67,Default,U,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.67,Default,A,0,0,0,,這次它噴火出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:20.22,Default,U,0,0,0,,她們為什麼到這種地方來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:24.20,Default,A,0,0,0,,糟糕了 燃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:28.64,Default,U,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.52,Default,U,0,0,0,,閃耀魔杖
