Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.27,Default,A,0,0,0,,好燙燙燙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:38.69,Default,U,0,0,0,,快念咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.49,Default,U,0,0,0,,唸出咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.45,Default,A,0,0,0,,魔杖它…
